fehbgnotes

________________________________________________________________________________

Add text from a notes.txt file to the wallpaper (the ~/.fehbg file needs to have been generated).

needs imagemagick.

usage:
  fehbgnotes
or:
  fehbgnotes [PATHTOFILE] [TEXTCOLOR] [TEXTSIZE]

the file from which notes are extracted can be set with the variable PATHTONOTES

can be installed by moving file to ~/.local/bin

  cp fehbgnotes ~/.local/bin
